{"tid":1137904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女導遊不滿東張西望近攝故施襲　金句王吳蕙芳：有咩唔見得光","createTime":"2019-05-04T07:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T07:32:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb91eb2ac888a092b3315d444c9e8673ac9166ab","tid":1137904,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】內地團逼爆影響各區居民生活，今年3月獲無綫電視（TVB）節目《東張西望》關注，女撰稿員拍攝在行人路駐足等候旅遊巴的內地團時，帶團惡導遊不滿，搶撰稿員手機及要求刪除片段，爭持間「搣」及刮到撰稿員手臂，致其瘀腫及擦損。導遊昨認罪，被裁判官質問「有乜嘢唔見得光呀」，最終獲判緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n不滿被拍 官：有乜唔見得光？<br />\n女被告萬明珠（39歲）昨日承認一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，指她於今年3月22日在紅磡陽光廣場附近犯案。<br />\n辯方求情指出，被告丈夫在國內任職地盤工，被告則從事導遊工作五年，與七歲兒子居港，因不滿被近距離拍攝才動怒犯案，導遊牌照或受本案影響。<br />\n主任裁判官吳蕙芳反問：「好近有乜嘢問題呀？使唔使咁嬲呀？有乜嘢唔見得光呀？」最終判被告監禁一個月，緩刑一年。<br />\n案情指25歲姓張事主是TVB資料撰稿員，當天早上約10時半她在崇安街一間朱古力店外以手機拍攝，當時被告帶領一團內地旅客光顧該店，之後在行人路等旅遊巴。其間被告不滿被拍攝，想搶走事主手機，施以「搣」功令事主感痛楚鬆手。事主嘗試搶回手機，過程中前臂被刮損，手機亦掉落地上。<br />\n事主拾起手機離開，準備會合在附近拍攝的同事，但被告死咬不放，一直追罵。事主以手機拍攝被告發難情況，待被告離開後報警。<br />\n警員到場後，朱古力店負責人指被告經常光臨，並提供其聯絡資料。被告返回現場時被捕，警誡下否認打人，稱是事主動手。<br />\n案件編號：KCCC981/19<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190504/20670650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F20670650&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW91KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=f4f88ab0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190504%2F20670650&h=41e6edd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190504/20670650</a>"},{"pid":"8f87702de22bb53fef852618afd665771d64ee45","tid":1137904,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da601f1f3b1ac1923b1019804eae68f719f3efac","tid":1137904,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f87702de22bb53fef852618afd665771d64ee45","tid":1137904,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190504/large/04la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190504%2Flarge%2F04la5p3.jpg&h=37c4ed4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告萬明珠昨承認一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。"},{"pid":"abdbad73d2b21408be6072e9b59f7e246890fd7f","tid":1137904,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"267ba555989ac4b25e05b46224a721c83dee7655","tid":1137904,"uid":44514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"bc2120e13a9bdcf51e6ec451d6825b3681cb2d61","tid":1137904,"uid":15880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"abdbad73d2b21408be6072e9b59f7e246890fd7f","tid":1137904,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da601f1f3b1ac1923b1019804eae68f719f3efac","tid":1137904,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f87702de22bb53fef852618afd665771d64ee45","tid":1137904,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190504/large/04la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190504%2Flarge%2F04la5p3.jpg&h=37c4ed4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告萬明珠昨承認一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"李慧琼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090e8880709f35b09e634021eb7105fe56abb02d","tid":1137904,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"警誡下否認打人，上到庭就認罪。坐一個月益左佢<img sr